  "text": "RNA was extracted and cDNA synthesized as previously described [CITATION_1] . Primer sequences for ASIC3, CGRP, COMT, SCN9A, SCN10A, TrkA, TRPA1, TRPV1, and TRPV4 were created for rat sequences by Integrated DNA Technologies (Coralvile, IA). All reactions were performed in triplicate, and all mRNA levels were normalized to GAPDH. ΔΔCT values were used to calculate fold change and relative expression levels.",
